PURPOSE:-
--------
To test the functionality of PC with Poll Save feature disabled.


SCENARIO:-
---------
All nodes are placed in a wireless subnet.
Node 1 is configured as AP/PC. Nodes 2 thru 10 are  configured as BSS stations.


              2     3    4

             5     1   6   7

              8   9     10



Application:
------------
FTP/GENERIC exchange is configured between:
Node 2 and 3 
Node 5 and 7 
Node 9 and 10 


RUN:-
----
Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet pc-poll-nosave.config'.



DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. pc-poll-nosave.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. pc-poll-nosave.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. pc-poll-nosave.nodes - QualNet node placement file for the simulation run.
4. pc-poll-nosave.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
5. README - This file.


